text: Biwanr is a town in Hamirpur District of Uttar Pradesh, India. == Geography == Biwanr is located approx 400 km from Delhi, the national capital. == Demographic view == India census, Biwanr had a population of 10386. Males constituted 5643 of the population and females 4743. Bewar has an average literacy rate of 64.3%. ==References== Biwanr Census Category:Cities and towns in India
